title: 2Stone Express
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, International, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Bakery, European, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Focus is on vegetarian food, with a few vegan choices. Some of the vegetarian items may be able to be made vegan; please inquire. Made-in-house pitas and tortillas are available; vegans please inquire. Pizzas are baked in a stone oven and offer plenty of fresh veggies and meat substitutes as toppings.
